    - Simulate 5 concurrent users Register new account on a Nopcommerce. Ramp up 10s to 5 users. Loading 1m, them ramp down in 10s.
    - Simulate 10 concurrent users to Login then browsing product, some of them add some products to cart. Each users run 5 iterations.
